title: Cafe Fuzion
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Thai, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small Asian food restaurant in a small shopping center. Menu green dot notes which dishes are or can be made veg. The noodles, fried rice, and curries come with choice of protein which includes tofu & veggies instead of meat. One pho can be veg. Some appetizers are also veg. Prices inexpensive to moderate.
